Comment: 0,0:00:00.27,0:00:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on and get moving, Hikki.
Comment: 0,0:00:02.82,0:00:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,R-right...
Comment: 0,0:00:26.97,0:00:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Now... Where should we start?
Comment: 0,0:00:35.47,0:00:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Comment: 0,0:00:38.56,0:00:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... How about the prom?
Comment: 0,0:00:41.23,0:00:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Comment: 0,0:00:43.77,0:00:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,To get right to the point, \Nthe school administration
Comment: 0,0:00:45.78,0:00:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,is heavily considering cancelling the prom.
Comment: 0,0:01:00.04,0:01:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, it's safe to say the organizers\Nwill be asked to refrain from any further planning.
Comment: 0,0:01:43.79,0:01:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can become one of the top dogs, then it's a blast!
Comment: 0,0:01:46.46,0:01:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You get free rein to do as you please.
Comment: 0,0:01:52.01,0:01:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Comment: 0,0:01:54.43,0:01:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as a problem isn't treated like a problem, it's not really a problem.
Comment: 0,0:01:57.81,0:02:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But once something is acknowledged as a problem,
Comment: 0,0:02:00.14,0:02:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,it's easier to give in and deal with it than to fight back against the fallout.
Comment: 0,0:02:00.77,0:02:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Bet she's doing other bad things, too lololol
Comment: 0,0:02:00.77,0:02:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,So wrong
Comment: 0,0:02:00.77,0:02:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever consider how the apple feels?
Comment: 0,0:02:00.77,0:02:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Wonder how much time she'll get?
Comment: 0,0:02:00.77,0:02:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That apple does look good tho
Comment: 0,0:02:00.77,0:02:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Waiting for the public apology Is she on social media?
Comment: 0,0:02:04.48,0:02:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Sooner or later, the opinions against prom and those requesting we cancel
Comment: 0,0:02:08.48,0:02:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,will be well-known to the students and the PTO.
Comment: 0,0:02:11.61,0:02:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,If that happens, then it's obvious that the anti-prom faction will gain strength...
Comment: 0,0:02:17.24,0:02:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's practically checkmate already.
Comment: 0,0:03:52.17,0:03:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You really do plan on making this prom a reality, don't you?
Comment: 0,0:03:55.84,0:03:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if that's a good thing or not, though.
Comment: 0,0:03:59.01,0:03:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Comment: 0,0:04:00.34,0:04:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yukinoshita doesn't want you to intervene.
Comment: 0,0:04:08.39,0:04:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're going to do it anyway, huh?
Comment: 0,0:04:10.73,0:04:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm used to girls not wanting my attention.
Comment: 0,0:04:19.78,0:04:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Comment: 0,0:04:20.78,0:04:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm kind of happy.
Comment: 0,0:04:23.33,0:04:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,However, Yukinoshita is also making every effort to change things.
Comment: 0,0:04:26.91,0:04:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to encourage her to do that.
Comment: 0,0:04:29.46,0:04:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I'm not sure if simply helping her is the right decision.
Comment: 0,0:04:33.50,0:04:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're talking about dependency and such, I think you have the wrong idea about us.
Comment: 0,0:04:37.59,0:04:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's something important to Yukinoshita.
Comment: 0,0:04:40.43,0:04:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,To her, this may be something like a trial she's imposed on herself.
Comment: 0,0:04:44.06,0:04:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,A trial?
Comment: 0,0:04:45.43,0:04:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Or a rite of passage, to put it in other words.
Comment: 0,0:04:50.98,0:04:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think that's blowing it out of proportion?
Comment: 0,0:04:52.65,0:04:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,No. I think that, well, stuff like that happens.
Comment: 0,0:04:55.53,0:04:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly. It happens often enough.
Comment: 0,0:04:57.57,0:04:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,From school entrance exams to job hunts,
Comment: 0,0:04:59.28,0:05:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,you may not even get a break from it all until you turn 30.
Comment: 0,0:05:01.66,0:05:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You know?
Comment: 0,0:05:02.78,0:05:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Eventually, you'll reach the period of life
Comment: 0,0:05:04.28,0:05:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,where you have to come face-to-face with yourself.
Comment: 0,0:05:06.54,0:05:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that go for you, too?
Comment: 0,0:05:08.04,0:05:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, of course.
Comment: 0,0:05:10.71,0:05:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,There were a lot of things that I wanted to do and become.
Comment: 0,0:05:14.88,0:05:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,There were also a lot of things I didn't want to do or become...
Comment: 0,0:05:19.38,0:05:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Each time I would choose carefully,
Comment: 0,0:05:21.72,0:05:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,try it out, screw it up, give up, and then choose again.
Comment: 0,0:05:25.30,0:05:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a cycle.
Comment: 0,0:05:26.93,0:05:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm still in it even now.
Comment: 0,0:05:28.89,0:05:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,With that in mind, let me ask you...
Comment: 0,0:05:30.39,0:05:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you intend to associate with her from now on?
Comment: 0,0:05:33.65,0:05:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,In any case, I don't consider disassociating from her an option.
Comment: 0,0:05:37.78,0:05:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Comment: 0,0:05:39.11,0:05:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,"I see"? Is that it?
Comment: 0,0:05:41.07,0:05:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough. I believe in you.
Comment: 0,0:05:43.49,0:05:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I appreciate that.
Comment: 0,0:05:45.45,0:05:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen up, Hikigaya.
Comment: 0,0:05:47.33,0:05:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't save her just by simply helping with the prom.
Comment: 0,0:05:51.66,0:05:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What matters is how you interact with her.
Comment: 0,0:05:54.33,0:05:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You get it, right?
Comment: 0,0:05:56.17,0:05:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't ask you for help anymore.
Comment: 0,0:05:58.92,0:06:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,This is pretty difficult.
Comment: 0,0:06:01.09,0:06:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's certainly not easy. Especially when it comes to you all.
Comment: 0,0:06:05.30,0:06:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,For sure.
Comment: 0,0:06:07.01,0:06:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Since this time our goals totally clash with each other.
Comment: 0,0:06:09.93,0:06:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey now, what are you talking about? What have you all been doing up until now?
Comment: 0,0:06:16.44,0:06:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a time-honored custom to settle conflicting opinions with...
Comment: 0,0:06:22.03,0:06:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,If you ask me, you should all have a little more faith
Comment: 0,0:06:24.78,0:06:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,in the experience that you've acquired for yourselves.
Comment: 0,0:06:29.70,0:06:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you're right.
Comment: 0,0:06:33.71,0:06:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,There's not much left to talk about now that you've got a plan of action.
Comment: 0,0:06:36.38,0:06:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yukinoshita should still be in the student council room.
Comment: 0,0:06:39.05,0:06:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Oh, one last thing...
