Comment: 0,0:09:42.69,0:09:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You're doing this for me?! What's going on, are you hitting on me?
Comment: 0,0:09:45.65,0:09:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I do like getting special treatment,
Comment: 0,0:09:47.48,0:09:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and I don't hate being saved when I'm in a pinch, but putting that all aside,
Comment: 0,0:09:50.36,0:09:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna need you to wait until things are cleared up. Sorry!
Comment: 0,0:09:53.16,0:09:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, okay. You're totally off-base, but you've got the gist of it.
Comment: 0,0:09:55.95,0:09:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with that reaction? I'm off-base, huh? Is that so?
Comment: 0,0:10:02.00,0:10:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you going through with this?
Comment: 0,0:10:03.50,0:10:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Comment: 0,0:10:04.25,0:10:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yukino is totally going to reject your help and
Comment: 0,0:10:06.88,0:10:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure Haru must have warned you against that, right?
Comment: 0,0:10:10.17,0:10:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So why are you pushing it?
Comment: 0,0:10:12.26,0:10:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Anybody in their right mind would avoid dealing with annoying stuff like this.
Comment: 0,0:10:16.80,0:10:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I have my reasons.
Comment: 0,0:10:20.27,0:10:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me a proper answer.
Comment: 0,0:10:24.19,0:10:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't feel like I can give a good explanation.
Comment: 0,0:10:28.19,0:10:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't mind.
Comment: 0,0:10:34.36,0:10:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my responsibility.
Comment: 0,0:10:36.37,0:10:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Your responsibility?
Comment: 0,0:10:38.83,0:10:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,This situation getting complicated, the worry about dependency in our relationship,
Comment: 0,0:10:41.41,0:10:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,and all of that stuff is my fault.
Comment: 0,0:10:43.54,0:10:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'll do whatever I have to do to set things right again.
Comment: 0,0:10:46.75,0:10:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all it is.
Comment: 0,0:10:51.59,0:10:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm sorry.
Comment: 0,0:10:53.51,0:10:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I kind of zoned out when I got a different answer than what I expected.
Comment: 0,0:10:58.30,0:11:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it. My uniform was pretty beaten up to begin with.
Comment: 0,0:11:01.72,0:11:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going to tell Yukino exactly what you just told me?
Comment: 0,0:11:08.27,0:11:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Just saying it should be easy enough, yeah.
Comment: 0,0:11:10.52,0:11:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But whether I'll get through to her or not is another question.
Comment: 0,0:11:12.86,0:11:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys are a real pain, you know...
Comment: 0,0:11:16.03,0:11:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Comment: 0,0:11:16.99,0:11:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Personally, having the service club assist the student council makes
Comment: 0,0:11:20.28,0:11:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,everything a whole lot simpler.
Comment: 0,0:11:21.99,0:11:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm counting on you to make this work.
Comment: 0,0:11:34.92,0:11:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But frankly, I don't think that will be enough to convince Yukino.
Comment: 0,0:11:39.05,0:11:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I figured. What is this conversation, an infinite loop?
Comment: 0,0:11:41.97,0:11:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But hold on, Irohas, can't you put in a good word for me or something?
Comment: 0,0:11:45.48,0:11:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Absolutely not.
Comment: 0,0:11:48.06,0:11:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't do that.
Comment: 0,0:11:49.31,0:11:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not? You didn't even really consider it...
Comment: 0,0:11:51.57,0:11:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I just can't. Girls don't change their minds once they've decided on something.
Comment: 0,0:11:55.99,0:11:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Though girls are quick to change their stance on whatever someone else decided,
Comment: 0,0:11:59.74,0:12:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and if things ever go south then we just play dumb.
Comment: 0,0:12:02.28,0:12:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Girls are the worst.
Comment: 0,0:12:04.45,0:12:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait... isn't that just YOU?
Comment: 0,0:12:07.00,0:12:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Student Council Room
Comment: 0,0:12:19.55,0:12:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Hikigaya.
Comment: 0,0:12:21.22,0:12:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Comment: 0,0:12:22.47,0:12:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Isshiki, want to take a break?
Comment: 0,0:12:24.72,0:12:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That sounds good.
Comment: 0,0:12:38.49,0:12:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you hear?
Comment: 0,0:12:39.45,0:12:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, yeah. I was with Yuigahama at the time.
Comment: 0,0:12:44.99,0:12:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Comment: 0,0:12:46.33,0:12:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I got the details from Miss Hiratsuka. Are you okay?
Comment: 0,0:12:50.37,0:12:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,If there's anything I can do I'll help you...
Comment: 0,0:12:52.75,0:12:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no need to worry. I'm also thinking about what move to make.
Comment: 0,0:13:13.48,0:13:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you plan to do?
Comment: 0,0:13:15.36,0:13:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,We're still discussing it right now.
Comment: 0,0:13:17.32,0:13:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,"Discussing it," huh?
Comment: 0,0:13:19.90,0:13:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,From what I heard, the school is only going to insist you voluntarily refrain from moving forward.
Comment: 0,0:13:23.16,0:13:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means, worst case, it's not impossible to outright refuse.
Comment: 0,0:13:25.87,0:13:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to make every effort to avoid that.
Comment: 0,0:13:28.33,0:13:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Since they want it to be a "voluntary" thing, it's easy enough to use that against them.
Comment: 0,0:13:31.37,0:13:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But if threatening that drastic measure is the only move you make,
Comment: 0,0:13:33.92,0:13:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,it won't be enough to convince them.
Comment: 0,0:13:35.21,0:13:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm aware of that. I plan to discuss things beyond that.
Comment: 0,0:13:39.59,0:13:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yukinoshita is without a doubt not going to try to force the prom to happen.
Comment: 0,0:13:44.97,0:13:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so, dangling that sort of self-destructive threat can be enough to win a spot at the negotiation table.
Comment: 0,0:13:48.93,0:13:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,can be enough to win a spot at the negotiation table.
Comment: 0,0:13:53.02,0:13:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The real problem is figuring out what terms are suitable to negotiate on.
Comment: 0,0:14:00.65,0:14:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You two came up with all this?
Comment: 0,0:14:03.03,0:14:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Our process has been more like, I eliminate the ideas that Yukino gives,
Comment: 0,0:14:06.99,0:14:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,and Yukino points out the flaws in my ideas.
Comment: 0,0:14:15.92,0:14:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep it classy
Comment: 0,0:14:16.96,0:14:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Dress code
Comment: 0,0:14:18.00,0:14:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,No uploading photos
Comment: 0,0:14:19.17,0:14:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Get an official photographer!!
Comment: 0,0:14:20.71,0:14:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And what's the chance of success with this?
Comment: 0,0:14:24.09,0:14:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,More than fair.
Comment: 0,0:14:25.89,0:14:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It addresses the demands they've made, and I'm working on a road map to assure the changes are implemented.
Comment: 0,0:14:28.22,0:14:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'm working on a road map to assure the changes are implemented.
Comment: 0,0:14:31.18,0:14:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think the odds are low for us at all.
Comment: 0,0:14:34.23,0:14:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I see.
Comment: 0,0:14:35.94,0:14:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're more or less going to follow their demands then they'll approve, huh?
Comment: 0,0:14:39.69,0:14:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,In normal circumstances.
Comment: 0,0:14:44.61,0:14:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,However, things aren't normal this time.
Comment: 0,0:14:47.95,0:14:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,They're intentionally finding faults with the intention of killing the prom.
Comment: 0,0:14:52.16,0:14:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not making demands because they want to improve the plan, or bring it to fruition.
Comment: 0,0:14:59.21,0:15:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yukinoshita, can I talk to you?
Comment: 0,0:15:02.01,0:15:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, there's space for me to intervene.
Comment: 0,0:15:05.88,0:15:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, I'll just go and-
Comment: 0,0:15:07.55,0:15:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Comment: 0,0:15:08.47,0:15:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,This is about prom, right? Then it's best if you stayed and listened.
Comment: 0,0:15:12.60,0:15:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... I guess you're right.
Comment: 0,0:15:18.31,0:15:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I help you with prom?
Comment: 0,0:15:28.57,0:15:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, I don't think your proposal is a bad one.
Comment: 0,0:15:31.33,0:15:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But I would say the odds of it working aren't very good.
Comment: 0,0:15:33.75,0:15:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why you should also come up with another plan.
Comment: 0,0:15:36.25,0:15:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Since I don't agree with your current idea, I'll also think of something.
Comment: 0,0:15:38.67,0:15:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the situation. It doesn't mean I'm going to do something to interfere.
Comment: 0,0:15:42.59,0:15:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll simply be moving as you instruct me to.
Comment: 0,0:15:44.88,0:15:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Just consider me as a wall you have to get your ideas over.
Comment: 0,0:15:47.51,0:15:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That way, it's no different from how you give instructions to Isshiki or the others, right?
Comment: 0,0:15:51.05,0:15:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been in a lot of situations like that. This is no different.
Comment: 0,0:15:57.98,0:15:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Comment: 0,0:16:00.61,0:16:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That's no different than how things have been.
Comment: 0,0:16:02.48,0:16:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then...
Comment: 0,0:16:03.28,0:16:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And when push comes to shove, I'll just end up depending on you.
Comment: 0,0:16:07.49,0:16:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That's exactly what I want to change.
Comment: 0,0:16:10.12,0:16:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You understand what my sister was trying to say, right?
Comment: 0,0:16:21.04,0:16:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Comment: 0,0:16:22.00,0:16:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,But I think I should also accept responsibility for that.
Comment: 0,0:16:26.01,0:16:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,If there's a problem with how we've been doing things, we'll find a different way to do things.
Comment: 0,0:16:29.89,0:16:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,or a different way of thinking, or way to interact or something.
Comment: 0,0:16:33.81,0:16:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Then... whatever the end result is, I want to take responsibility for it.
Comment: 0,0:16:39.31,0:16:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So... I... want...
Comment: 0,0:16:45.65,0:16:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,...to save you.
Comment: 0,0:16:56.41,0:16:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Comment: 0,0:16:57.87,0:17:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's okay. Just hearing that is enough.
Comment: 0,0:17:02.00,0:17:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. I got it. I won't say anymore.
Comment: 0,0:17:06.51,0:17:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't help you out.
Comment: 0,0:17:08.51,0:17:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Comment: 0,0:17:10.43,0:17:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,However, I'm not saying that I won't go against you.
Comment: 0,0:17:14.47,0:17:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-what?
Comment: 0,0:17:16.06,0:17:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what to do when you and I have a difference of opinion, don't you?
Comment: 0,0:17:22.77,0:17:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,A showdown to see which one of you can do the most acts of service!
Comment: 0,0:17:31.66,0:17:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't sit right with me if prom doesn't happen after I half-assed my involvement in it.
Comment: 0,0:17:36.79,0:17:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,However, there's no way I can agree with the way you're doing things.
Comment: 0,0:17:39.71,0:17:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, I'll have to do this myself.
Comment: 0,0:17:42.87,0:17:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you serious about what you're saying?
Comment: 0,0:17:44.42,0:17:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Our showdown isn't over yet.
Comment: 0,0:17:46.42,0:17:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no reason for the entire Service Club to be bound by one single method.
Comment: 0,0:17:49.55,0:17:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why it's okay if you and I do things differently.
Comment: 0,0:17:53.80,0:17:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I wrong?
Comment: 0,0:17:57.43,0:17:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That should be fine, right?
Comment: 0,0:18:00.43,0:18:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Either way is fine with me. I don't care what process you use as long as the prom happens.
Comment: 0,0:18:05.73,0:18:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... I'm not saying this because I want permission. I'm just going to do it anyways.
Comment: 0,0:18:13.57,0:18:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though she hates losing,
Comment: 0,0:18:15.49,0:18:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure if she'll go along with this even after I brought up the showdown.
Comment: 0,0:18:22.12,0:18:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then...
Comment: 0,0:18:24.33,0:18:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoever loses the showdown will have to do one thing the winner says.
Comment: 0,0:18:29.76,0:18:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that work for you?
Comment: 0,0:18:35.34,0:18:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Sounds good.
Comment: 0,0:18:43.94,0:18:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What's that mean? That's creepy.
Comment: 0,0:18:46.15,0:18:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,H-hey...
Comment: 0,0:18:47.56,0:18:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, it is kinda creepy and I don't get what you mean...
Comment: 0,0:18:50.86,0:18:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And what's with that smug look?
Comment: 0,0:18:54.11,0:18:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that definitely is a bit creepy.
Comment: 0,0:18:57.74,0:18:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, right?
Comment: 0,0:18:59.16,0:19:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey now...
Comment: 0,0:19:02.41,0:19:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,This is essentially a confession.
Comment: 0,0:19:05.21,0:19:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That, or a lover's quarrel, or maybe a break up.
Comment: 0,0:19:08.59,0:19:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Having to listen to it right next to them, I felt like an idiot.
Comment: 0,0:19:13.42,0:19:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It felt like being forced to realize just how irrelevant I am.
Comment: 0,0:19:17.18,0:19:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It kind of annoyed me.
Comment: 0,0:19:19.68,0:19:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It would make anyone want to hurl a little insult like, "That's creepy."
Comment: 0,0:19:23.64,0:19:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, I really want him to take responsibility.
Comment: 0,0:19:27.85,0:19:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Just to confirm...
Comment: 0,0:19:29.11,0:19:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do things my way, and you do things your way to make the prom happen.
Comment: 0,0:19:33.94,0:19:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Comment: 0,0:19:35.11,0:19:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The winner of this competition will get to make one request of the loser. Is that correct?
Comment: 0,0:19:41.08,0:19:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Comment: 0,0:19:42.20,0:19:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, uh... I guess I didn't expect you to go along with this. Right?
Comment: 0,0:19:47.79,0:19:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,None of my business.
Comment: 0,0:19:49.75,0:19:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not really that much of a mystery.
Comment: 0,0:19:52.34,0:19:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you know? I hate losing.
Comment: 0,0:19:58.59,0:20:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously, I never imagined their talk would get this complicated while somehow being so clear and precise.
Comment: 0,0:20:01.85,0:20:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,complicated while somehow being so clear and precise.
Comment: 0,0:20:04.89,0:20:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,And if he fed that line to me with such a serious face, I don't know what I'd do.
Comment: 0,0:20:13.90,0:20:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,For real reals, I want him to take responsibility. He's never done that once so far.
Comment: 0,0:20:22.41,0:20:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,But still, I don't want him to just say,
Comment: 0,0:20:24.91,0:20:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,"It's my responsibility" like it's some frivolous excuse.
Comment: 0,0:20:28.54,0:20:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hachiman, Yukino, and Yui are all a pain in the butt,
Comment: 0,0:20:32.13,0:20:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,but I'm a pain in the butt in my own way, too.
Comment: 0,0:20:35.88,0:20:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously, they're all pains.
Comment: 0,0:22:16.52,0:22:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, should we head home soon?
Comment: 0,0:22:19.44,0:22:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see. I'm going to stay here a little longer, so you can go ahead and leave.
Comment: 0,0:22:25.28,0:22:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay...
Comment: 0,0:22:27.87,0:22:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And go ahead and call a meeting for the student council members starting tomorrow.
Comment: 0,0:22:31.91,0:22:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Comment: 0,0:22:32.71,0:22:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I-isn't it too early for that? We just decided how we'll go about this today.
Comment: 0,0:22:37.75,0:22:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have it all firmed up by tomorrow.
Comment: 0,0:22:40.01,0:22:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, the prom will surely happen. So it's better we have more time to prepare, yes?
Comment: 0,0:22:46.34,0:22:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You're declaring victory, huh?
Comment: 0,0:22:48.05,0:22:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Comment: 0,0:22:52.48,0:22:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't push yourself too hard.
Comment: 0,0:22:56.23,0:22:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Comment: 0,0:22:57.77,0:22:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's not a problem.
Comment: 0,0:23:03.49,0:23:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right, though.
Comment: 0,0:23:06.99,0:23:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,This will be the last one. I can truly end things with this.
Comment: 0,0:23:10.70,0:23:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! I'm heading out! Oh, please lock up when you leave!
Comment: 0,0:23:13.87,0:23:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. See you tomorrow.
Comment: 0,0:23:26.59,0:23:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The Yukino I saw when I looked back...
Comment: 0,0:23:31.18,0:23:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,...looked like she was crying.
Comment: 0,0:23:35.69,0:23:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, jeez, everyone is such a pain! Why are they like this?
Comment: 0,0:23:38.23,0:23:40.90,NextWeek,,0,0,0,,And what was he even talking about? How complicated does he have to make this?!
Comment: 0,0:23:40.90,0:23:43.28,NextWeek,,0,0,0,,I mean, his personality has always been beyond complicated...
